  BANDWIDTH - a musical experience.
  jtnimoy,2011
  
  INSTRUCTIONS
  Turn up your sound volume.
  Click and drag to explore.
  Press bubbles to change scenes.
  Press Escape to quit.
  
  
  Made possible by the Sandwell Arts Trust
  Special thanks:
     the OpenFrameworks project
